        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>April 63d/68</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Faithful to my,<lb/> promise, I solicited subscriptions<lb/> to your
                publications, but have<lb/> only succeeded in procuring a<lb/> single name. There
                appears<lb/> (as you so clearly explained to<lb/> me, a want of manifest
                inte<lb/>rest in Jewish publications, and<lb/> still less appreciation of
                Jewish<lb/> authors. When oh when will<lb/> you receive the reward which your<lb/>
                labours so e<add>?</add> entitle<lb/> you to receive. I fear not until<lb/> a new
                spirit is infused in the<lb/> heart of <placeName>Israel</placeName>.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Pardon me, (it may be <sic>presumtuous</sic>)<lb/> if I solicit a reply to this.
                My<lb/> inordinate thanks for the espousal<lb/> of <placeName>Judea's</placeName>
                cause makes me<lb/> bold enough to ask a correspondence<lb/> from
                    <placeName>Judea's</placeName> guide.<lb/> Hoping that you are in the<lb/>
                enjoyment of the best of health<lb/> and an agreeable <date>Pesach</date>,<lb/> I
                subscribe myself</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Your very ob'dt</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Simon Bachrach</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Care of <persName>Rev. Dr. Lilienthal</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName><sic>Cincinatti</sic> O.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Send 1 Vol. Meditations &amp; Prayers to<lb/>
                <persName>Coblen's &amp; Co.</persName><lb/>
                <placeName>180 Lexington St.</placeName></p>
            <p>Price $2.50</p>
        </body>
